Class.name: HoleFoods.KPIYears
Class.Description: This KPI class provides the list of values for the Years pivot variable of the HoleFoods cube.

XData.name: KPI
XData.Data:
<kpi name="HoleFoodsYears" displayName="HoleFoodsYears" sourceType="mdx" mdx="SELECT [DateOfSale].[Actual].[YearSold].CURRENTMEMBER.Properties("Key") ON 0,NON EMPTY [DateOfSale].[Actual].[YearSold].Members ON 1 FROM [HOLEFOODS]" >
<property name="Value" displayName="Value" columnNo="1" />
</kpi>
